Installation Instructions
*************************


Requirements
============

crand requires:
	* the ncurses library
	* the gcc compiler


Installation
============

Simple install procedure:

	$ tar -xzvf birthday-date-*.tar.gz	# unpack sources
	$ cd birthday-date-*.tar.gz		# change directory to crand sources
	$ ./configure				# run the "configure" script
	$ make					# build crand
	[ become root if necessary ]
	$ make install				# install crand

